<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="G.C3.A9ographie">Géographie</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Charleroi&amp;veaction=edit&amp;vesection=1" title="Modifier la section : Géographie" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Charleroi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Modifier la section : Géographie">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
