<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Limites_de_la_ville">Limites de la ville</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Charleroi&amp;veaction=edit&amp;vesection=2" title="Modifier la section : Limites de la ville" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Charleroi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Modifier la section : Limites de la ville">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Les communes limitrophes de Charleroi sont&#160;:</p>
